General Electric Co, railcar leasing unit complete di $178.5 million buy of similar businesses from Leucadia National Corp and Brae Corp na 74% owned by Leucadia di seller.

Di buyer na GE Capital Railcar Services, Chicago wey be one major owner of railway equipment, and part of GE Capital Operations.

Leucadia, New York, estimated it had a pre-tax gain of $57 million plus part of the brae's gain.

Because of tax lassos carry forward, Leucadia say e dey expect make government reduce tax on top "some of di gain".

Di total gain for Brae na $15 million plus seven million naira tax, di sellers con talk sey dis money na because de don give deir income tax wey be sey de dey pay higher income tax wey be sey de dey pay before.

